import React from 'react'
import { Paper, ListItem, TextField, Grid } from '@material-ui/core'

function LoginForm() {
    return (
        <Paper>



            <form>
                <Grid direction="column" align-items="flex-end">
                    <Grid>


                        <TextField id="outlined-basic" label="Username" variant="outlined" labelWidth={30} />
                        <TextField id="outlined-password-input"
                            label="Password"
                            type="password"
                            autoComplete="current-password"
                            variant="outlined" />
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>

            </form>


        </Paper>

    )
}

export default LoginForm
